Author: wrak54
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Ubex Concludes Agreements With Key SSPs  The Ubex project has successfully concluded 10 agreements with Supply Side Platforms for the provision of traffic volumes in various regions around the world. After the successful conclusion of an agreement with the Yandex Advertising Service, Ubex has concluded 10 more agreements with key SSPs to ensure large traffic volumes for users of the platform. The SSP platforms operate in every key region of the world and will provide the Ubex platform with full coverage of millions of users. The conclusion of the agreements will ensure that the Ubex platform will have outstanding traffic volumes and will be able to ensure that all of its users will have global coverage in ad placement.

Author: lonesomestranger
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Header Bidding On Ubex SSP  ''The Ubex project has included Header Bidding on the platform’s SSP to increase the quality of ads and ensure fairer competition among users.  Header Bidding is an exchange built into an SSP. The only difference is that in a Header Bidding exchange, the highest bid wins. It is an auction of the first price, not the second as is the case with exchanges. ''  Check it out: https://medium.com/ubex/header-bidding-on-ubex-ssp-2916ce4f2237

Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Finally received my tokens but now I'm even more pissed off at something else they've quietly changed on their website which is another broken promise of the ICO:  "Ubex has the possibility (but not the obligation) to buy back UBEX Tokens and burn them"  The ICO clearly stated that UBEX *WOULD* use 20% of all profits to buy back and burn tokens until there were only 2bn left in circulation.  Now they've backtracked on this as well.  Just posting this as a warning for anyone else thinking of investing.  Don't is my strong opinion.  They think they can just treat their investors like dirt now they have their money.  Disgraceful.  ETA: I'm requesting the FIAT value I paid for my tokens back from UBEX.  You can't change such a fundamental promise like the above.  I suggest everyone else does the same.

Author: miroslav44
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: ^^ Just as a follow up.  Here is the exact wording from their website during the ICO (use wayback machine if you want to verify):   "Every quarter, we will use 20% of our proceeds from transaction commissions to buy back UBEX Tokens and destroy them, until 50% of all UBEX Tokens are taken out of circulation. This approach creates a scarcity in the token supply."   Here is the current post-ICO wording:  "Ubex has the possibility (but not the obligation) to buy back UBEX Tokens and burn them. UBEX Tokens would be taken out of circulation, this would create a scarcity in the token supply."   I think Ubex have some explaining to do.  Livid.

Author: Computron83
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: I think we need to prepare for the painful realization that UBEX just might be a SCAM. Nobody seems to have received their UBEX tokens yet, and there is no info from the Ubex company.  Also, take a look on the overview of UBEX holders on Ethplorer:  https://ethplorer.io/address/0x6704b673c70de9bf74c8fba4b4bd748f0e2190e1#transfers=4&tab=tab-holders  There is just ONE account that holds almost ALL the 72% percent of tokens that should have been distributed to the investors.  Also, there is no news on their FaceBook account, no new info on their medium account, no news on their website...no nothing.  Well, it might be something else too. They might be holding on to all the tokens for a while, to create a shortage of tokens and manipulate the market, so they can sell a small surplus of tokens on the public exchanges. Then, after a few days, they release the tokens to the ICO investors. In which case the Ubex price will go down a lot.  In any case, Ubex has a lot of explaining to do. I do fear however, that we will never receive any explaination from them.

Author: yuvadeep
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: The Ubex main aim is to solve all the problems faced in purchasing goods in digital advertising.  Ubex wants to create a global advertising ecosystem that builds on the trust and save from waste materials.  Advertisers who want to purchase the ad slots can book a slot with the help of the Ubex system. Blockchain-based smart contracts help in reducing risks to the users. Ubex Programmatic advertising creates different methods for purchasing advertisements online. To make decisions about transactions they started using some automated systems and algorithms. These transactions can be done without any involvement of a human and by the uniqueness of a population, age, education level, income etc and behavioral data about users available for the platform and the advertiser. When a user visits a web page, where he can see the ads that are available on the webpage.  For the fraction of seconds, you can see website starts loading and the system study the formation of the audience of the website. Thus, it starts matching the data with the client that points and selects the proper advertising format. Later, the auction controls among the advertisers who point out the audience, mainly to the visitor of the website and to those who want to show their advertising on the internet. During the period of the auction, the highest price and the winners are selected in this auction process. The winner who won in the advertisement is uploaded to the website and later shown to the user. The total process of big data processing and holding an auction takes place within 100 to 200 milliseconds. The total amount of work is done by the algorithms and the results are controlled only by the human. As per Magna Global, in the year of 2015, the size of the global advertising reached $465 billion, $493 billion in 2016 and when it comes to 2017 it crossed about $500 billion.  Compare with television advertising, you can see the internet advertising is exceeded and reached a size of $192 billion for the first time.

Author: miroslav44
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: I'm very concerned by this decision to extend the ICO...  It just doesn't make sense to me.  As the token is now listed they could have simply finished the ICO as scheduled and distributed the tokens.  If they needed more funds due to the price drop in ETH then they could have sold the additional tokens from their '10% reserve' on the exchanges themselves, rather than by extending the ICO.  The only explanation I can think of why they didn't do this is because they're expecting a massive dump of tokens on distribution and the price to plummet.   Which leads to several other concerns...  Who is currently trading UBEX on the exchanges bearing in mind the tokens haven't been distributed yet?    On these exchanges why is UBEX trading at 0.000045 ETH/UBEX?  This is 450% higher than the ICO price.  Why would anyone buy at this price when you can still purchase on the ICO for 80% less than this?  Why did they wait to liquidate the accumulated ETH?  Seems very foolish and essentially gambling that the price would be higher on completion.  If they'd liquidated it as the ICO was running they'd have received the average price smoothed over this period of time.  Far less risky.   A further concern I have is that the "Total raised" counter on the website doesn't seem to be accurate in reflecting purchases using BTC and LTC.  I saw around a week ago in the ticker window that someone had purchased tokens with 2 BTC which should have added around 36 ETH to the counter.  It never seemed to register this.  The value didn't increase at all from an hour before this alleged purchase and never incremented an amount close to 36 ETH in the hours afterwards.  Perhaps these purchases are only added at the end of each day or something.  If this is the case it's odd because the tokens are credited to your account almost immediately as I found out when I purchased some with LTC.  Be great if a representative form Ubex could alleviate some of these concerns.  Personally I'm starting to regret participating.

Author: miroslav44
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: My concerns only get deeper.  Why are there 4 different instances of the UBEX token on the ETH blockchain all with a total supply of 4bn?  All have some distributed holders  https://etherscan.io/token/0x6704b673c70de9bf74c8fba4b4bd748f0e2190e1 https://etherscan.io/token/0xdfca93ab244fbcab952581881534737cf7c4a129 https://etherscan.io/token/0xa9868c4a302883f557f8fd616a4b9cc1a0aa6c59 https://etherscan.io/token/0xcc757889b8992c0ae378e2e025197ff44e0e406c   I go back to why the extension of the ICO mathematically doesn't make sense.  Ubex are trying to raise an extra 4800 ETH.  In doing this they've given away an extra 10% compensation bonus on what has already been invested by the community.  Equivalent to 2400 ETH.  So if they sell all the additional tokens (4800 ETH), the absolute maximum they can be better off by is 10% (2400 ETH) plus any increase in the price of ETH.  If they only sell half the additional tokens during the extension and the price of ETH remains the same then they are in exactly the same position they are now (but down 20% of tokens as the unsold 10% would be burned).  If they sell all the additional tokens and the price of ETH drops a further 10% (only $28!) then they are in exactly the same position they are now (but down 10% of tokens).  They could have ended the ICO as scheduled and sold an additional 10% of tokens on the exchanges themselves.  This would have raised the same extra amount, would have kept investors happy and they would have 10% more tokens left in the reserve overall.  So I'm sorry mathematically this just doesn't make sense.    Please someone correct me if I'm wrong.

Body: UBEX Artificial intelligence: under the hood https://medium.com/ubex/ubex-artificial-intelligence-under-the-hood-3123975296b2  What does UBEX actually try to achieve? Deliver the advertisement to customers, but not simply show any popup with an ad, but show only the ad the customer could be interested in. If the level of interest is low, it is possible not to show an annoying advertisement at all. Isn’t it a good idea? It is a great idea! All of us are so tired of contextual advertisement, the future advertisement should be different! The main task, as we can see, is to measure the level of a customer’s interest to understand the possible set of interested advertisement materials.

Author: cryptonis33
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Ubex is a global decentralized advertising exchange, operating fully on the basis of neural networks with the use of blockchain and smart contracts. Ubex allows passage from the traditional pay per click scheme to the model of payment for targeted actions, the most fair and interesting model for advertisers. At the heart of Ubex’s advertising purchasing algorithms, lie neural networks that process information about each visitor to the member networks’ websites. The neural networks evaluate the interests of users, calculate the likelihood of targeted actions for all advertiser offers, and choose the most suitable advertisement. Thanks to this, member network website visitors see only those ads that are maximally confined to their interests, and which would convince them to fulfill the target action with maximum probability. Thus, Ubex maximizes the targeting of advertising and the economic efficiency for advertisers. https://icomarks.com/ico/ubex

Author: baronofficiall2
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Today's problems for users, advertisers and publishers in the advertising industry; High pay for production and service due to the display of irrelevant and irritating advertisements, multiple mediators and high commissions, high costs for fraudsters due to compelling and provocative advertising methods. Uncertainty results because advertisers are forced to pay for clicks and ads without the guarantee of real sales, difficulty in determining all available channels, and ineffectiveness of advertising channels after the budget is spent. We can list the time losing to find an advertiser, low earnings, unpredictable payments from advertisers, payment delays or non-payments. Ubex aims to solve the problem of low confidence in the purchase of digital advertisements. Smart contracts make it as transparent and fair as possible for advertisers and publishers (owners of ad space on sites), as well as reducing the risks for all parties the least. Ubex understands the needs of the current market and knows that it will take a long time before decentralized solutions are put into the market by applying such an approach, providing a pay-per-click plan, a pay model for targeted actions, the most fair and interesting model transition for advertisers. Google Inc., Facebook Inc. and others are only able to pass decentralized solutions in the very distant future, and this poses a serious risk for successful development. For this reason, Ubex supports both a fully hybrid approach to interaction with traditional DSPs and DMPs, as well as decentralized solutions, as well as multi-currency offers and cryptographic currencies. However, the most important difference is that Ubex is not only a place for algorithmic traffic purchases, but is based on artificial intelligence in a central role in the system. Although a number of projects, such as Exchain and MAD, declare an AI presence in their own systems, the role played by them is marginal. Ubex AI constantly improves the quality of its ad purchases, enables it to detect fraudulent content, and ultimately shows more relevant ads to the user. For this purpose, publishers' data mining is included as a function within the system. Ubex is a decentralized global ad place where companies effectively advertise, and publishers are able to profitably toss their advertising space at their source. Its mission is to create a global advertising ecosystem of common trust and maximum effectiveness. By using nerve networks and accumulated data, advertisers 'bids and publisher websites' interaction will allow a user to select the most relevant ad content at a particular time, maximizing the likelihood of getting the desired results. Applying smart contracts for all types of tracking will remove all indirect links between advertisers and publishers, thereby increasing the economic efficiency of the collaboration, which will help reduce commissions significantly by removing the intermediaries. In order for publishers to create an opportunity to specify their ad space, the advertiser will use the existing statistics in the exchange process to generate potential earnings and an opportunity to pre-aggregate if the rating is high enough. It will allow you to implement a system that scales advertisers to be stored with the full history of their activities to prevent fraud on the block-chain and to enable a mechanism for establishing relationships with the most trusted partners.

Author: peterkate630
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Advertisers can set up and run ad campaigns using the Ubex platform. The user specifies the cost of advertising, or a percentage of the sale, as well as deferred payment. Widgets can be personalized by the advertiser and can also be provided by the exchange. After setting up the widget, the advertiser sets the rules for displaying the ads so that they appeal to the target audience as possible. In parallel with the settings, the neural network provides forecasts of the effectiveness of the customized advertising campaign. The advertiser can monitor in real time all the key metrics for the created advertising campaign.  Publishers can connect their advertising slot to the Ubex advertising platform and start earning as soon as the tracking add-on accumulates enough data about site traffic for further analysis by the neural networks.  The Ubex platform will provide opportunities not only to publishers and advertisers, but also to companies that need regression analysis of user data. The system’s neural core, which is responsible for making decisions at all stages of the life cycle of the advertising material, will have an API, access to which can be provided to partner companies.

Author: gartmah
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Ubex Welcomes Ali Kassab as Advisor https://medium.com/ubex/ubex-welcomes-ali-kassab-as-advisor-c3c83ef68d0f  Ubex is pleased to announce that Ali Kassab has agreed to join the Ubex project team as an Advisor and will be lending his efforts in promoting the project.  Ali Kassab is a French national and a self-made businessman & a serial entrepreneur with over 20  years of experience across multinational cloud software companies and digital payment companies in the MENA region. His expertise lies in nurturing and building entrepreneurship ecosystems in the MENA region from ground zero to multi-million businesses. He is a known innovator and technology enthusiast.  His early experiences at leading retail and telecoms companies across the region shaped his later business ventures — including international sales, ICT, marketing, and consultancy — in the Middle East. He has led successful projects in Europe, North Africa and the Middle East region, mainly for leading telecom operators ( Etisalat, du, Orange, Vodafone), financial companies (ADIB, AXA, HSBC), and governments (ADDC, AADC, DED). Ali believes strongly in empowering people, process and customer experience to ensure company growth and sustainability. And as Dubai powers its way to become the first Blockchain Capital of the world. Centurion & Co. UAE’s leading investment and advisory firm under Ali’s leadership co-founded and helped launched an ICO, the country’s first decentralized app which allows users to pay for a range of services with cryptocurrencies. Over the months, Ali has established a successful model for ICO’s to secure their execution and launch.  The Ubex project team is certain that Ali’s addition to the Advisory Board will help increase the value of the platform and promote it in the MENA region.

Author: S3cco
Title: [ANN] UBEX.com - Global Decentralized Advertising Exchange
Body: Bitcoin Garden: Ubex Project Token Sale Soft Cap Reached in One Day https://bitcoingarden.org/ubex-project-token-sale-soft-cap-reached-in-one-day/  The Ubex project, a pioneering global advertising exchange platform, has launched its Token Sale and raised its soft cap in less than 1 day.  The Ubex project launched its Token Sale on the 21st of May, 2018, and it will last until the 13th of August. The Ubex Token Sale is unique on the blockchain market as it provides equal contribution opportunities and bonuses for all participants. In addition, the Ubex project refrained from conducting any private sale or presale rounds to ensure equal terms for all participants and to exclude any speculation or preference factors.  The project soft cap was reached during the first day of the Token Sale and has already exceeded the 4000 ETH mark....
